p: The current study aimed to identify the oily matters of T. pruinosum chemical composition using Gas Chromatography-Mass Spectroscopy (GC-MS) method of isolated by new microwave-ultrasonic-reactor extractor apparatus technique. In addition to that, the current study aimed to evaluate the antioxidant, cytotoxicity, and cyclooxygenase inhibitory activities of T. pruinosum VO.
